        "Name": "Redback Maelstrom",
        "Details": "One of the rare designs produced by the ill-fated Clan Widowmaker, the Maelstrom—known as the Redback among the Clans—was popular with Widowmaker Mechwarriors after Operation Klondike. The design mounted an Enhanced ER PPC, a Clan standard ER large laser, two SLDF surplus medium pulse lasers and a prototype ER medium laser.  Given the quantity produced by Clan Widowmaker and the advantages the mech had at the time it saw limited production with several of the surviving clans and survived to be used as a Solahma and garrision units.\n\n <b><color=#e51717>Pafftek Industries Sub-mod</color></b>",
